<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module css]]
.danke{
padding: 5px 5px 5px 15px;
margin-bottom:10px;
width: 100%;
font-family: monospace;
font-size: 1.1em; }

.agent{
background-color:#002200;
border: 3px solid #55AA55;
color: #77CC77;
}

.site{
background-color:#222200;
border: 3px solid #AAAA55;
color: #DDDD77;
}
[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><strong>重要</strong>：这部分应置于文字框出现的位置。</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[div class=&quot;danke agent&quot;]]
| 细节
| 细节
| 细节
| 细节
| 细节

