文本
更多文本

更多[[span class=&quot;blinkbar&quot;]][][[/span]]

[[/div]]
[[/div]]
[[/div]]</code>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项6</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-7" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-7')">7</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>
<div class="tape-wrap">
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">播放</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">重播</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="tape-anim">
<div class="tape-left"></div>
<div class="tape-right"></div>
</div>
<div class="tape-record">
<p><span class="record r1"><em>第一行</em><br />
<em>第二行</em><br />
<em>最后一行</em></span><br />
<span class="record r2"><em>文字</em><br />
<em>更多文字</em></span></p>
