<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki:component:classified-decoration</span><br />
|lv=<strong>1</strong>/<strong>2</strong>/<strong>3</strong>/<strong>4</strong>/<strong>5</strong><br />
