<p><a style="font-size: 18px; color: white; text-shadow: 1px 3px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); text-decoration: none;" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/niveaux-de-menace-des-objets-scp" target="_blank"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; background-color: black; text-align: center; border: 1px none #000; margin: 1px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px;"><strong>威胁等级：</strong>黑色</span></a></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><sup>（点我！）</sup></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;其他颜色……</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;关闭</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><a style="font-size: 18px; color: black; text-shadow: 1px 3px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); text-decoration: none;" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/niveaux-de-menace-des-objets-scp" target="_blank"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; background-color: #f3f3f3; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #080808; margin: 1px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px;"><strong>威胁等级：</strong>白色</span></a><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<a style="font-size: 18px; color: white; text-shadow: 1px 3px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); text-decoration: none;" href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/niveaux-de-menace-des-objets-scp" target="_blank"><span style="display: inline-block; width: 100%; background-color: #b01; text-align: center; border: 1px none #000; margin: 1px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px;"><strong>威胁等级：</strong>红色</span></a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[a href=&quot;*http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/niveaux-de-menace-des-objets-scp&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 18px; color: white; text-shadow: 1px 3px 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); text-decoration: none;&quot;]]
[[span_ style=&quot;display: inline-block; width: 100%; background-color: black; text-align: center; border: 1px none #000; margin: 1px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px;&quot;]]
**威胁等级：**黑色
[[/span]]
[[/a]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><strong>注意：</strong>要改变颜色，只需将“background-color”设为<span class="ruby">白/蓝/绿/黄/橙/红/黑<span class="rt">white/blue/green/yellow/orange/red/black</span></span>色。具有高/低对比度的颜色可能会需要你更改文字<span class="ruby">颜色<span class="rt">color</span></span>为<span class="ruby">白/黑<span class="rt">white/black</span></span>色来增强可读性。</p>
<p><strong>注意：</strong>此格式最适合与其它替代标题格式配合使用，如前文所示。此格式基于法国分部的威胁等级分类。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项6：</span></strong></p>
