<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">复制这些：</span></strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<h3><span>链接选项：将你目标页面的网址（或&quot;/&quot;加上页面名称）写到&quot;url&quot;后面</span></h3>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include</span> :scp-sandbox-3:component:login-module <strong>|url=<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-style-resource</span></strong>|id=&lt;你的ID&gt;|pw=&lt;你的密码&gt;|disc=true<strong>|value=链接</strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<h3><span>折叠选项：将要显示的文字写到折叠块中</span></h3>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:component:login-module&#32;|id=&lt;你的ID&gt;|pw=&lt;你的密码&gt;|disc=true]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[collapsible&#32;show=&quot;折叠&quot;&#32;hide=&quot;登出&quot;]]</span><br />
文字<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/collapsible]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<h3><span>其它……？</span></h3>
<table class="wiki-content-table">
<tr>
<th>参数</th>
<th>是否必填</th>
<th>允许的值</th>
<th>描述</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>id</td>
<td><strong>是</strong></td>
<td>文字</td>
<td>ID值</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>pw</td>
<td><strong>是</strong></td>
<td>文字</td>
<td>密码值</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>url</td>
<td>否</td>
<td><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">http://example.com</span><br />
/pagename</td>
<td>当为空<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-22" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-22')">22</a></sup>时，链接按钮将不会出现</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>value</td>
<td>否</td>
<td>文字</td>
<td>链接按钮上的文字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>disc</td>
<td>否</td>
<td>true<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-23" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-23')">23</a></sup></td>
<td>当不为空时，密码将不会被显示</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>title</td>
<td>否</td>
<td>文字<br />
链接</td>
<td>标题文字</td>
</tr>
</table>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<h2 id="toc9"><span>自定义插图方块格式</span></h2>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项1</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-24" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-24')">24</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://smlt.wikidot.com/local--files/mrpines:choo-choo/train3.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="enlarge" alt="train3.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>将鼠标移至图片上方来放大。</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:image-zoom&#32;name={$name}|caption={$caption}|width=300px|align=right]]</span></p>
</div>
<p>将<strong>{$name}</strong>改为指向图片的文件名或链接。将<strong>{$caption}</strong>改为图片下方所显示的文字描述。图片的宽度（width）及对齐方式（align）都被设定为标准SCP文档格式，但它们同样可以被修改。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项2</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-25" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-25')">25</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://smlt.wikidot.com/local--files/mrpines:choo-choo/train3.jpg" style="width:300px;" class="unblur" alt="train3.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>将鼠标移至图片上方来查看。</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:image-blur&#32;name={$name}|caption={$caption}|width=300px|align=right]]</span></p>
</div>
<p>将<strong>{$name}</strong>改为指向图片的文件名或链接。将<strong>{$caption}</strong>改为图片下方所显示的文字描述。图片的宽度（width）及对齐方式（align）都被设定为标准SCP文档格式，但它们同样可以被修改。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项3</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-26" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-26')">26</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>



<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:300px;"><img src="http://smlt.wikidot.com/local--files/mrpines:choo-choo/train3.jpg" title="Click and hold to enlarge." style="width:300px;" class="fillpg" alt="train3.jpg" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:300px;">
<p>按住不放来放大图片。</p>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-sandbox-3:component:image-zoom-2&#32;name={$name}|caption={$caption}|width=300px|align=right]]</span></p>
</div>
<p><strong>重要：</strong>如果你的文件扩展名不是.png或.jpg的话，此组件将无法正常工作。</p>
<p>将<strong>{$name}</strong>改为指向图片的文件名或链接。将<strong>{$caption}</strong>改为图片下方所显示的文字描述。图片的宽度（width）及对齐方式（align）都被设定为标准SCP文档格式，但它们同样可以被修改。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span></p>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<h2 id="toc10"><span>图像轮播框</span></h2>
<div class="carousel-container center" style="width: calc(300px + 34px);"><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/local--code/component%3Acarousel/1#?images=nintendo.jpg,youtube.jpg,linkedin.png,rescue.png,billwurtz.jpg&amp;wiki=scp-sandbox-3&amp;page=carousel-demo&amp;interval=3&amp;background=white&amp;options={$options}" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width: calc(300px + 34px); height: calc(240px + 6px);"></iframe>
<div class="carousel-caption-wrapper">
<div class="carousel-caption {$no-caption}" style="width: calc(300px);">
<p>一些并没有深层含义或隐藏信息的图片。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>



