<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include</span> :smlt:7happy7:ut-ver2<br />
|home=你的沙盒主页地址<br />
]]</p>
</blockquote>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<h2 id="toc12"><span>黑条格式</span></h2>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项1</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-31" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-31')">31</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>
<p><span class="bblock">这个格式使你能够创建黑条信息并在鼠标移过时显示该信息。</span></p>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[span class=&quot;bblock&quot;]]文字[[/span]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><strong>如何调整：</strong></p>
<p>以下代码用于调整文字显示时的颜色</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module CSS]]
.bblock:hover {color: white}
[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项2</span></strong></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>
<p><span class="dblock">这个选项在鼠标移过时改变背景而不是文字的颜色。</span></p>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[span class=&quot;dblock&quot;]]文字[[/span]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><strong>如何调整：</strong></p>
<p>以下代码用于调整背景改变时的颜色</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module CSS]]
.dblock:hover {background: #f4f4f4}
[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<h2 id="toc13"><span>“今日日期”格式</span></h2>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项1</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-32" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-32')">32</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>



<h2><span>普通（显示至“分”）</span></h2>
<div class="normalFontTime">
<p>例子：今天是<iframe src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/1" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="120" class="" style=""></iframe>。</p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;normalFontTime&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">例子：今天是[[iframe&#32;http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/1&#32;width=&quot;120&quot;&#32;scrolling=&quot;no&quot;]]。</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;其它……</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<h2><span>普通（显示至“秒”）</span></h2>
<div class="normalFontTime">
<p>例子：<iframe src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="130" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;normalFontTime&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">例子：[[iframe&#32;http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/2&#32;width=&quot;130&quot;&#32;scrolling=&quot;no&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<h2><span>h1（显示至“分”）</span></h2>
<p>例子：<br />
<iframe src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/3" align="" frameborder="" height="25" scrolling="no" width="230" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[iframe&#32;http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/3&#32;width=&quot;230&quot;&#32;height=&quot;25&quot;&#32;scrolling=&quot;no&quot;]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<h2><span>h1（显示至“秒”）</span></h2>
<p>例子：<br />
<iframe src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/4" align="" frameborder="" height="25" scrolling="no" width="260" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[iframe&#32;http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/4&#32;width=&quot;260&quot;&#32;height=&quot;25&quot;&#32;scrolling=&quot;no&quot;]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<h2><span>粗体（显示至“分”）</span></h2>
<div class="normalFontTime">
<p><strong>例子：</strong><iframe src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/5" align="" frameborder="" height="16" scrolling="no" width="140" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;normalFontTime&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[iframe&#32;http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/5&#32;width=&quot;140&quot;&#32;height=&quot;16&quot;&#32;scrolling=&quot;no&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
<h2><span>粗体（显示至“秒”）</span></h2>
<div class="normalFontTime">
<p><strong>例子：</strong><iframe src="http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/6" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="160" class="" style=""></iframe></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[div&#32;class=&quot;normalFontTime&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[iframe&#32;http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/6&#32;width=&quot;160&quot;&#32;height=&quot;16&quot;&#32;scrolling=&quot;no&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/div]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>如何导入：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>重要：</strong>这部分应置于页面顶端：</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module css]]
@import url(http://scp-sandbox-3.wikidot.com/local--code/component:todaysdate/7);
[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p>导入了以上代码后，你就准备好了！现在你可以使用iframe了。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项2</span></strong></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<blockquote>
<p>今天是<span class="odate time_1610179685 format_%25Y%2F%25m%2F%25d">09 Jan 2021 08:08</span>……也许吧！</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module ListPages limit=&quot;1&quot; category=&quot;*&quot; order=&quot;updated_at desc&quot;]]
&gt; 今天是%%updated_at|%Y/%m/%d%%……也许吧！
[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<br />
