<h2 id="toc15"><span>Wikidot模块延展</span></h2>
<div style="text-align: center;">
<h3 id="toc16"><span>ListUsers模块</span></h3>
</div>
<p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项1（<em>为非Wikidot用户准备的ListUsers模块</em>）：</span></strong></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>
<div class="textchange">

<div class="sitemember">
<p><span style="color: blue">游客</span></p>
</div>
</div>



<p><strong>注意：</strong>如果你是wikidot用户，<strong>这个模块会显示你的ID</strong>；如果不是，<strong>它就会显示“游客”</strong>。</p>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="color: red">[[include :topia:listusers-1 users=&quot;.&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">##red|</span><strong>%%name%%</strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">##</span><br />
<span style="color: red">[[include :topia:listusers-2]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">##blue|</span><strong>游客</strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">##</span><br />
<span style="color: red">[[include :topia:listusers-3]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<br />
<strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">选项2（<em>包含ListUsers的变量的<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include]]</span>方法</em>）：</span></strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-33" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-33')">33</a></sup>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-34" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-34')">34</a></sup></p>
<div class="textchange">

<div class="sitemember">
<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-3935/school.png" style="width:100%;" alt="school.png" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:100%;">
<p>SCP-XXXX而且……我不知道你是谁。</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>



<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p><span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[module&#32;ListUsers&#32;users=&quot;.&quot;]]</span></span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:topia:inc-loop&#32;c=__________|p=&lt;include来源&gt;]]</span><br />
|&lt;value&gt;=<strong>%%name%%</strong><br />
]]<br />
<span style="color: red"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[/module]]</span></span></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>例子：</strong><br />
<span style="color: red">[[include :topia:listusers-1 users=&quot;.&quot;]]</span><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:topia:inc-loop&#32;c=__________|p=component:image-block]]</span><br />
|name=<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-3935/school.png</span><br />
|align=center<br />
|width=100%<br />
|caption=SCP-XXXX……而且你是<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">//</span><strong>%%name%%</strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">//</span>。<br />
]]<br />
<span style="color: red">[[include :topia:listusers-2]]</span><br />
[[include component:image-block<br />
|name=<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/scp-3935/school.png</span><br />
|align=center<br />
|width=100%<br />
|caption=SCP-XXXX而且……我不知道你是谁。<br />
]]<br />
<span style="color: red">[[include :topia:listusers-3]]</span></p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
