<h2 id="toc17"><span>ACS版头（Anomaly Classification System, 异常分类系统）</span></h2>
<p><a href="/anomaly-classification-system-guide">点击这里来看看这是干什么的。</a></p>
<p><strong>原作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404096); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404096&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610148452" alt="Woedenaz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404096)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/woedenaz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404096); return false;">Woedenaz</a></span></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>



<div class="anom-bar-container item-XXXX clear-# euclid none vlam 警告 {$american} lang-cn">
<div class="anom-bar">
<div class="top-box">
<div class="top-left-box"><span class="item"><span class="lang-cn">项目编号：</span><span class="lang-tr">項目編號：</span></span><span class="number">XXXX</span></div>
<div class="top-center-box">
<div class="bar-one"></div>
<div class="bar-two"></div>
<div class="bar-three"></div>
<div class="bar-four"></div>
<div class="bar-five"></div>
<div class="bar-six"></div>
</div>
<div class="top-right-box">
<div class="level"><span class="lang-cn">等级</span><span class="lang-tr">等級</span>#</div>
<div class="clearance"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="bottom-box">
<div class="text-part">
<div class="main-class">
<div class="contain-class">
<div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">收容等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">收容等級：</span></div>
<div class="class-text">euclid</div>
</div>
<div class="second-class">
<div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">次要等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">次要等級：</span></div>
<div class="class-text">none</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="disrupt-class">
<div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">扰动等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">擾動等級：</span></div>
<div class="class-text">vlam</div>
</div>
<div class="risk-class">
<div class="class-category"><span class="lang-cn">风险等级：</span><span class="lang-tr">風險等級：</span></div>
<div class="class-text">警告</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="diamond-part">
<div class="danger-diamond"><a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/classification-committee-memo">备忘录链接</a><br />
<div class="arrows"></div>
<div class="octagon"></div>
<div class="quadrants">
<div class="top-quad"></div>
<div class="right-quad"></div>
<div class="left-quad"></div>
<div class="bottom-quad"></div>
</div>
<div class="top-icon"></div>
<div class="right-icon"></div>
<div class="left-icon"></div>
<div class="bottom-icon"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><a href="/component:anomaly-class-bar">完整说明请点击这里。</a></p>
<blockquote>
