]]</p>
</blockquote>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<br />
<br />
<h2 id="toc18"><span>电子邮件模版</span></h2>



<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-35" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-35')">35</a></sup></p>
<div class="email-example">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">访问SCiPNET邮件？一&nbsp;(1)&nbsp;封新邮件！</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">回复：主题</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div style="text-align: left;">
<div class="email">
<div class="tofrom">
<p><strong>至：</strong>收件人<br />
<strong>自：</strong>发件人<br />
<strong>主题：</strong>主题</p>
</div>
<hr />
<p>文本</p>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div class="email">
<div class="tofrom">
<p><strong>至：</strong>收件人<br />
<strong>自：</strong>发件人<br />
<strong>主题：</strong>回复：主题</p>
</div>
<hr />
<p>文本</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>复制这些：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>重要</strong>：这部分应置于页面顶端</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module CSS]]
.email-example .collapsible-block-folded a.collapsible-block-link {
    animation: blink 0.8s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}
@keyframes blink {
    0% { color: transparent; }
    50%, 100% { color: #b01; }
}
.email {border: solid 2px #000000; width: 88%; padding: 1px 15px; margin: 10px; box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.email-example a.collapsible-block-link {font-weight: bold;}
.tofrom {margin-left: 10px; margin-top: 5px; padding: 1px 15px; border-left: solid 3px maroon}
[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><strong>重要</strong>：这部分应置于电子邮件出现的位置</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[div class=&quot;email-example&quot;]]
[[=]]
------
[[collapsible show=&quot;访问SCiPNET邮件？一 (1) 封新邮件！&quot; hide=&quot;回复：主题&quot;]]
[[&lt;]]
[[div class=&quot;email&quot;]]
[[div class=&quot;tofrom&quot;]]
**至：**收件人
**自：**发件人
**主题：**主题
[[/div]]
------
文本
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class=&quot;email&quot;]]
[[div class=&quot;tofrom&quot;]]
**至：**收件人
**自：**发件人
**主题：**回复：主题
[[/div]]
------
文本
[[/div]]
[[/&lt;]]
[[/collapsible]]
[[/=]]
[[/div]]</code>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p><br /></p>
<div style="border-bottom:2px solid #777; margin-bottom:1px;"></div>
<div style="border-bottom:1px solid #777;"></div>
<br />
<br />
<h2 id="toc19"><span>淡出的页面内容</span></h2>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>选项1</strong></span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-36" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-36')">36</a></sup></p>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>



<div style="padding-left: 1em">
<p>正常内容</p>
<div class="fadeout-wrapper">擦除内容
<p><span class="escape">正常内容</span></p>
<p>擦除内容</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">点击淡出</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">&nbsp;</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<div class="cover"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>正常内容</p>
</div>
<br />
<strong>复制这些：</strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;show&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">–&nbsp;hide&nbsp;block</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:125%;"><strong>CSS模块</strong></span></p>
<p>可以使用变量来自定义一些元素。</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>[[module css]]
@import url('http://smlt.wdfiles.com/local--code/ukwhatn%3Afadeout/1');

/*== 变量 ==*/
:root {

  /* 背景颜色（默认：white） */
  --fadeout-background: white;

  /* 淡出持续时间 */
  --fadeout-time: 1s;

  /* 剪裁页眉（来消除页眉下方的阴影）
      如果你使用默认Sigma-9以外的版式，请修改此变量。 */
  --cropped-header: url(http://smlt.wdfiles.com/local--files/ukwhatn:fadeout/header-crop.png);

}

[[/module]]</code>
</pre></div>
<p><span style="font-size:125%;"><strong>淡出部分</strong></span></p>
<p>只有“fadeout-wrapper”内的元素会被擦除。<br />
<strong><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[span&#32;class=&quot;escape&quot;]]文本[[/span]]</span></strong>不会被擦除。此元素可以使用任意次数，无大小限制。</p>
<div class="code">
<pre>
<code>正常内容

[[div_ class=&quot;fadeout-wrapper&quot;]]

擦除内容

[[span class=&quot;escape&quot;]]正常内容[[/span]]

擦除内容

[[collapsible show=&quot;点击淡出&quot; hide=&quot; &quot;]]
[[div class=&quot;cover&quot;]]
@@@@
[[/div]]
[[/collapsible]]
[[/div]]

正常内容</code>
</pre></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>选项2：在淡出后显示图片</strong></span><sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-37" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-37')">37</a></sup>
<p><strong>它是什么样的：</strong></p>
<div style="padding-left: 1em">
<p>正常内容</p>
<div class="fadeout-wrapper">擦除内容<br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span>
<div class="collapsible-block">
